[{"tablename":"text.sql","select":"select
  ts,
  sum(amount) as amount,
  count(*) as cnt,
  count(distinct transaction_id) as num_transactions
from (
select
  concat(
    to_date(event_time),
    ' ',
    lpad(cast(date_part('hour', event_time) as string), 2, '0'),
    ':',
    lpad(cast(date_part('minute', event_time) as string), 2, '0')
  ) as ts,
  transaction_id,
  amount
from fraudulent_txn
) as q
group by ts
order by ts","columns":[{"name":"ts","type":"STRING","isdim":true,"alias":"ts"},{"name":"amount","type":"BIGINT","isdim":false,"alias":"amount"},{"name":"cnt","type":"BIGINT","isdim":false,"alias":"cnt"},{"name":"num_transactions","type":"BIGINT","isdim":false,"alias":"num_transactions"}]}]
